  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bc0\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bb0 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd  \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b95\u0ba8\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Suspects of murder of millionaire woman arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police say that the father of the woman's daughter's husband and another person have been arrested on suspicion of murdering a 64-year-old woman who lived alone in a large house near the intersection of Kandy Lake Circle.",
        "According to the police, the two arrested suspects, aged 52 and 62, belong to Kadawati and Telkoda areas.",
        "Also, the knife used to kill the woman was recovered from the back of the suspect's house in Thelgoda area.",
        "On the 14th, at 2 o'clock in the afternoon, this woman was brutally murdered by slitting her throat.",
        "He said that the reason for the murder was due to the non-distribution of the property of the said woman to her children.",
        "The Kandy Headquarters Police Crime Branch is conducting further investigations into the incident."
      ],
